<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Service Unavailable</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #ff6347;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Sorry, it's not in Tunisia</h1>
        <p>
            We apologize, but the service you are trying to access is not available in Tunisia at the moment. 
            However, we have a variety of other services that may be of interest to you. 
            Please explore our website to discover more about what we offer.
        </p>
        <a href="/">Go to Homepage</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
